rComments: Lectures are made very interesting. Very approachable and takes a lot of interest in student to make sure they are learning. Had fun taking this class

Polycarpou was a nice guy, but did not appear qualified to teach this class.  There were way too many topics on the syllabus, so by the last week he was covering a chapter per lecture, and not really explaining anything.    My midterm was graded poorly, and the final did not reflect course material.  Overall poor course organization.
